These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, blue, pink
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes pink is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes green is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | green | blue | pink   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, salsa, funk
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
3. the fan of salsa is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | indie | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, amber, turquise
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | brown | turquise  | amber       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, accountant, dressmaker
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the dressmaker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Job   | dressmaker | paramedic | accountant     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, british
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the british##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the chinese##1
3. the british is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the chinese is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality         | pakistani | chinese     | british |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, electrician, bartender
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| Job   | freelancer       | electrician | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
House: cottage, craftsman, modern
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the craftsman house##1
3. the cottage house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| House           | cottage | modern | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, peach, pomegranate
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, dahlia
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person eating peach is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | dahlia | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, epic
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | horror | mystery  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
City: liverpool, venice, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| City   | venice | liverpool | paris |

