.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, card-games, video-games
1. the fan of trance is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Hobby   | video-games    | filmmaking | card-games |

