1. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| House   | futuristic    | cape-cod     | wooden   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

