The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker
1. the journalist is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
