.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, zinnia
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Flower   | lily    | zinnia | bellflower |
| Pet   | hedgehog | chinchilla     | fish        |

