3 different games are played: scrabble, go, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya   | garlic        |
| Game   | go    | scrabble | mah-jongg |

